Description

Achieve a contemporary look and garner compliments on your casual days in the Casandra espadrille wedge.
Leather and textile upper.
Pull-on design.
Crisscrossing elastic straps at instep.
Round toe.
Textile lining.
Textile and synthetic footbed.
Jute-wrapped wedge.
Synthetic sole.
Imported.
Measurements:

 Heel Height: 2 1⁄2 in
 Weight: 9 oz
 Platform Height: 1⁄2 in


Product measurements were taken using size 9, width B - Medium. Please note that measurements may vary by size.
Check out this comfort-enhancing accessory: 




