Rated:5 stars!
Style:
Rated:5 stars!


Was this review helpful?




Bought these in May of 2016. I am very particular about the fit of my shoes (I ordered 6 pair and returned 5, including the Ralph Lauren Cecilia, a similar style!) These fit great. I generally wear a 10.5, but most shoes do not come in this size and an 11 ends up being too large. I bought the size 10, in blue to match a custom-made dress, and they are a perfect fit. After a year of wearing them (not too often due to their color), they are just now looking a little worn on the bottoms, but they will make it another season.


