I was a little hesitant after ordering these online and then picking them up, they seemed a little too soft and I wasn't sure how well I would do sleeping on them as I'm used to pillows that are a little more firm. Since using them, I notice that I actually sleep better. They are sooo soft (but they don't sink into nothing when you lay on them- they actually keep their depth, if that makes sense). I would honestly say that these are the best pillows that I've ever owned and I won't be using anything but them from now on.
