Purchased on Black Friday thinking that the price was unbelievable for "Down Alternative" pillows. Ordered 3 medium firm, king sized. Turns out, these are not down alternative but fiber filled. Good for propping up but way too much loft for a good night's sleep. Would not recommend if you are looking for real DA pillows.



