Product Q&A
1 discussion : 1 answer


What color is the logo on the medium density pillow? I need to order two more to match the ones I have but I am not at home.

10 months ago

Podes
VA


The medium density pillows have a dark blue logo. The firm density pillows have a tan logo. The extra firm pillows have a light blue logo.
8 months ago

